AFDatabase.Description: Condition Based Maintenance for Pumps with Asset Based PI

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Horsepower
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT [Horsepower (BHP)] FROM [OSIDemo_Pump Manufacturer Information] WHERE Manufacturer = @Manufacturer

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Installation Date
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT [Installation Date] FROM [OSIDemo_CMMS Data (Maintenance Information)] WHERE [Serial Number] = '%Element%'

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Pump Type
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT Type FROM [OSIDemo_Pump Manufacturer Information] WHERE Manufacturer = @Manufacturer

AFAttributeTemplate.Name: Serial Number
AFAttributeTemplate.ConfigString: SELECT [Product Name] FROM [OSIDemo_Pump Manufacturer Information] WHERE Manufacturer = @Manufacturer

AFAnalysisRule.VariableMapping: Efficiency||Calculated Efficiency;[GUID]||{bb686f90-6078-4a55-967f-73fb5552ccb1};AverageTemp||Daily Average Bearing Temperature;[GUID]||{f9dfa5a7-4699-4c31-b2e8-ffaeb6172f45};HourlyMaxFlowRate||Hourly Maximum Discharge Flow Rate;[GUID]||{3cb60bc6-9641-4b74-b9f3-624dc6af5b68};[GUID]||[UNSET];

AFAnalysisRule.ConfigString: Status := IF '{706d2b90-67c6-463a-80ea-3826fa90b4df};Current Draw' > 1 AND '{8bb47700-1775-4ec1-b084-8cbf74449c9b};Pump Status' = "OFF" THEN "ON" ELSE IF '{706d2b90-67c6-463a-80ea-3826fa90b4df};Current Draw' < 1 AND '{8bb47700-1775-4ec1-b084-8cbf74449c9b};Pump Status' = "ON" THEN "OFF" ELSE IF '{706d2b90-67c6-463a-80ea-3826fa90b4df};Current Draw' > 1 AND '{8bb47700-1775-4ec1-b084-8cbf74449c9b};Pump Status' = "ON" THEN NoOutput() ELSE IF '{706d2b90-67c6-463a-80ea-3826fa90b4df};Current Draw' < 1 AND '{8bb47700-1775-4ec1-b084-8cbf74449c9b};Pump Status' = "OFF" THEN NoOutput() ELSE IF TagBad('{8bb47700-1775-4ec1-b084-8cbf74449c9b};Pump Status','*') THEN "OFF" ELSE NoOutput();
